'''史蒂文斯理工學院'''（{{lang-en|'''Stevens Institute of Technology'''}}，縮寫：{{lang|en|'''SIT'''}}）是位於美國[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[霍博肯_(新澤西州)|霍博肯]]的一所[[私立大學|私立]][[研究型大學|研究型大學]]，坐落於[[哈德遜河|哈德遜河]]河畔隸屬於[[紐約都會區|紐約都會區]]，由美國工程師、企業家{{Link-en|埃德溫·奧古斯都·史蒂文斯|Edwin Augustus Stevens}}的遺產捐助創立於1870年，<ref name="history">{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.stevens.edu/sit/about/history.cfm
 |title       = A Brief History
 |accessdate  = 27 February 2009
 |publisher   = Stevens Institute of Technology
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20111103194853/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/about/history.cfm
 |archivedate = 2011年11月3日
}}</ref> 是美國最古老的[[理工學院|理工學院]]之一、美國{{Link-en|獨立科技大學聯盟|Association of Independent Technological Universities}}（Association of Independent Technological Universities）的創始院校之一，也是美國最早開始專門研究[[機械工程|機械工程]]的學院。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family/stevens-institute-of-technology |title=Hoboken Historical Museum - Stevens Institute of Technology |publisher=hobokenmuseum.org |date= |accessdate=2014-04-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419230023/https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family/stevens-institute-of-technology |archivedate=2014-04-19 }}</ref> 除去霍博肯的主校區外，它於[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]還有一個分校區。主校區緊鄰紐約曼哈頓，讓它被評為全美大學最佳地理位置第3名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.niche.com/colleges/search/best-college-locations/|title=2019 Best College Locations in America|publisher=Niche|accessdate=2019-04-14|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402173747/https://www.niche.com/colleges/search/best-college-locations/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

這所理工學院有超過五千名、來自數十個國家的學生。大學內有三所[[卓越中心|卓越中心]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=The National Center for Secure & Resilient Maritime Commerce|url=http://www.stevens.edu/csr/|accessdate=5 December 2011|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201205419/http://www.stevens.edu/csr/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="President's Report 2010">{{cite web|title=The President's Report 2010|url=http://www.stevens.edu/sit/sites/default/files/Stevens-President-Report-2010.pdf|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=21 May 2012|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924110516/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/sites/default/files/Stevens-President-Report-2010.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Research Centers">{{cite web|title=Research Centers|url=http://www.stevens.edu/research/centers.html|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=5 December 2011|archive-date=2013-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118093343/http://www.stevens.edu/research/centers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而[[諾貝爾物理學獎|諾貝爾物理學獎]]得主[[弗雷德里克·萊因斯|弗雷德里克·萊因斯]]是該校校友，該校的教員[[歐文·朗繆爾|歐文·朗繆爾]]亦曾獲得[[諾貝爾化學獎|諾貝爾化學獎]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nobelprize.org |title=Nobelprize.org |publisher=Nobelprize.org |date= |accessdate=2011-11-16 |archive-date=2012-02-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65IoQQxWE?url=http://www.nobelprize.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

