=== 早期 ===

1784年，[[約翰·史蒂文斯_(發明家)|約翰·史蒂文斯]]買下了今史蒂文斯大學所在的土地<ref name=FamilyHistory>{{cite web|title=The Stevens Family|url=https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family|publisher=Hoboken Historical Museum|accessdate=23 May 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501133207/https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family|archivedate=2015年5月1日}}</ref><ref name=History>{{cite web|title=About Stevens: A Brief History|url=http://www.stevens.edu/sit/about/history.cfm|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=2 December 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103194853/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/about/history.cfm|archivedate=2011年11月3日}}</ref>，他以發明及經商發家，他們傢後來成爲了當地世族。他的兒子羅伯特和埃德溫·史蒂文斯是美國最早的商業鐵路運營者。<ref name=Family_Legacy>{{cite web|title=The Stevens Family|url=https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family/legacy|publisher=Hoboken Historical Museum|accessdate=23 May 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404112828/https://www.hobokenmuseum.org/history/the-stevens-family/legacy|archivedate=2015年4月4日}}</ref><ref name=History />

埃德溫在1868年逝世，按其遺囑，他的包括土地在内的遺產將被用來建立一所教育機構。<ref name="Edwin’s_Will">{{cite web|title=Will of Edwin A. Stevens|url=http://librarycollections.stevens.edu/items/show/661|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=23 May 2015|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411220244/http://librarycollections.stevens.edu/items/show/661|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 埃德溫的遺孀瑪莎·埃德溫是其遺囑執行人。於是，史蒂文斯理工學院在1870年作爲一所專門教授[[機械工程|機械工程]]學知識的學員正式開學。<ref name=History/> 學院辦學模式依循歐洲同類理工學院的傳統。<ref name=History /> 除去機械工程之外，他還授予化學及物理博士學位，因此而成爲美國最早的博士授課點之一。<ref name="Morton Memorial">Franklin D. Furman, ''Morton Memorial:A History of Stevens Institute of Technology'' New Jersey: Stevens Institute of Technology, 1905, p. xi</ref> 1880年，該學院的第一位機械工程學教授[[羅伯特·H·瑟斯頓|羅伯特·H·瑟斯頓]]成爲了[[美國機械工程師學會|美國機械工程師學會]]第一任會長。<ref>American Society of Mechanical Engineers. [http://www.asme.org/Communities/History/Resources/Thurston_Robert_Henry.cfm "Thurston, Robert Henry"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.asme.org/Communities/History/Resources/Thurston_Robert_Henry.cfm |date=20101225164517 }}. Retrieved 2010-04-20.</ref>

=== 現代 ===
[[二戰|二戰]]期間，該學院是參與美國[[V-12海军学院培训计划|V-12海军学院培训计划]]的131所學院之一，<ref name="stevens-v-12">{{cite web |url=http://www.stevens.edu/alumni/News_&_Publications/Alumniletter/ALMay_June03/Features/Alumni_Weekend_stories/V12.htm |title=V-12 program to mark its 60th anniversary at Stevens |publisher=[[Hoboken,_New_Jersey|Hoboken, New Jersey]]: Stevens Institute of Technology, Stevens Alumni Association |last= |first= |accessdate=September 29, 2011 |year=2003 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040906110842/http://www.stevens.edu/alumni/News_%26_Publications/Alumniletter/ALMay_June03/Features/Alumni_Weekend_stories/V12.htm |archivedate=2004年9月6日 }}</ref> 實際上有一艘住宿船“SS Stevens Victory”就是以該學院的名字命名的，<ref name="The Last Voyage of the SS Stevens">{{cite journal
 |date=Fall 1975 | title = The Last Voyage of the SS Stevens | journal = Stevens Indicator | volume = 92 | issue = 4 | pages = 3, 10 | publisher = Stevens Alumni Association }}</ref> 而這艘船已經是該學院的標誌之一。<ref name="SS Stevens to sail for scrap pile">{{cite news | title = SS Stevens to sail for scrap pile
 | work = [[Jersey_Journal|Jersey Journal]] | date = 1975-08-25 | accessdate = }}</ref>

1967年，史蒂文斯理工學院開始接受女性入學。1971年正式成爲[[男女共學|男女共學]]的學院。雖然1975屆的學生中只有19名女性，但40多年之後，該學院女學生比例已經達到25%。<ref name="Women's History">{{cite web|title=Forty Years of Women at Stevens: First Female Students Pioneered the University’s Future|url=http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/forty-years-women-stevens-first-female-students-pioneered-university%E2%80%99s-future|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=21 May 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034537/http://www.stevens.edu/news/content/forty-years-women-stevens-first-female-students-pioneered-university%E2%80%99s-future|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1982年該學院成爲美國首家要求所有新生購置電腦的大學。<ref name="Lore-El">{{cite web|url=https://www.stevens.edu/sit/residence-life/housing-options/lore-el-center|title=Lore-El Center|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|date=|accessdate=2015-05-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428202643/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/residence-life/housing-options/lore-el-center|archivedate=2015-04-28}}</ref>

