該大學規模較小，共有四個學院，即工程和科學院（Charles V. Schaefer, Jr. School of Engineering and Science）、系統和企業學院（School of Systems and Enterprises）、商學院（School of Business）和文藝學院（College of Arts and Letters）。本科生專業29個，師生比為7:1。<ref name=UndergradViewbookIntro>{{cite web|title=Introduction|url=http://www.stevens.edu/sit/sites/default/files/Stevens-Undergraduate-Viewbook.pdf|work=2011-2012 Undergraduate Viewbook|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=21 May 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610061518/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/sites/default/files/Stevens-Undergraduate-Viewbook.pdf|archivedate=2012年6月10日}}</ref><ref name=UndergradAdmissions>{{cite web|title=Undergraduate Admissions|url=http://www.stevens.edu/sit/admissions/academics/index.cfm|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814095656/http://www.stevens.edu/sit/admissions/academics/index.cfm|archivedate=2012-08-14|accessdate=2016-03-25}}</ref> 此外史蒂文斯理工學院還有43個碩士課程、22個博士課程。<ref name=Prospectus_Academics>{{cite web|title=Stevens Innovators and Leaders|url=http://issuu.com/stevensadmissions/docs/graduate_prospectus#download|work=Graduate Prospectus|publisher=Stevens Institute of Technology|accessdate=21 May 2012|page=4,22–30|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315185425/https://issuu.com/stevensadmissions/docs/graduate_prospectus#download|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

